{"tid":699924,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟邊個國家既民族優秀得過日本?","createTime":"2018-06-13T02:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-16T08:28:12.000Z","uid":26931,"like":10,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f18063728f3433932c3b7e26dc94c8bda8377ad2","tid":699924,"uid":26931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:27:32.000Z","msg":"從民族意識，公民素質，文化發展，同群眾能力水平去計<br />\n<br />\n以前細過以為英法澳好好，點知原來英國佬先係最唔識禮儀既，法國佬就大量又臭寸又多罪犯，澳洲人勁鍾意睇唔起人唔識尊重人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n美國可能大家對佢期望不高，反而冇咁令人失望，但整體都係低日本好多<br />\n<br />\n亞洲方面，中國俄羅斯依啲唔洗講，韓國人都係廢，星馬泰坡可能反而唔差，但都稱唔上好好<br />\n<br />\n究竟有邊個國家拍得住日本? 大國黎講德國有冇得鬥? 細國就挪威瑞士丹麥冰島?"},{"pid":"b4022339d605739f0a0f2afc8fa168a072aa5285","tid":699924,"uid":48577,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:35:46.000Z","msg":"香港人"},{"pid":"febbe5a6bb5f8d17ef0119426d4f00670adb2797","tid":699924,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:38:23.000Z","msg":"中國或成為最大得益者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd449373f6fc0751a99606c7de1ffeb3213871c1","tid":699924,"uid":61105,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:41:48.000Z","msg":"瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"361141416d07313f26df8d01078df79d2a17c02f","tid":699924,"uid":36547,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:42:17.000Z","msg":"德國"},{"pid":"4f78ce83722fb643b943eb700b8fa94439f18a70","tid":699924,"uid":105678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:46:07.000Z","msg":"之前去台南旅遊撞到個日本人<br />\n<br />\n咁啱大學take過course識講兩句日文，就諗住同佢吹下水啦<br />\n<br />\n個日本仔講英文還好，有禮得體，發現你識日文就好似轉咗channel咁，串過馬撚<br />\n<br />\n自此撞親日本仔都凝住凝住唔講日文"},{"pid":"93a082986dea79b4d143cdb74d4f351085d995b6","tid":699924,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f78ce83722fb643b943eb700b8fa94439f18a70","tid"